<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich XVI. und Albrecht II. von Schwarzburg, Herren zu Leutenberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Marquart Waltmann, Diener der Stadt, in nicht genannter Angelegenheit an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_120" id="58v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_120_r2l1"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Grauen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r2l2">cʒu <expan>Svvarcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Lüthenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_120_r2l4">Gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Als vns ewr 
<del rend="strikethrough">gnade </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_120_r2l3">edell </ab></add> <expan>yecʒunde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r2l5">hat / darümb <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>Markart<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r2l6">waltman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener <expan>weiſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dicʒ briefs / vnd <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r2l7"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell waʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener Darümb cʒu <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r2l8">mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_120" id="58v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>,
                        graven czu <expan>Swarczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu <expan>Lüthenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als uns ewr <add>edell</add>
<expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, darümb
                                <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gnaden <expan>Markart<ex>en</ex></expan> Waltman,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, <expan>weis<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dicz briefs, und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell, waz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener darümb czu
                            <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade
                        werb von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
